%% Models as a Service - Component Structure Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

graph TB
    subgraph "Models as a Service (MaaS)"
        API["maas-api<br/>Go/Gin REST API<br/>Port 8080"]
        TierMap["tier-to-group-mapping<br/>ConfigMap"]
        API -->|reads| TierMap
    end

    subgraph "Gateway Layer (openshift-ingress)"
        Gateway["maas-default-gateway<br/>Gateway API Gateway<br/>HTTP/80, HTTPS/443"]
        AuthPolicy["gateway-auth-policy<br/>Kuadrant AuthPolicy<br/>TokenReview + SAR"]
        MaaSAuthPolicy["maas-api-auth-policy<br/>Kuadrant AuthPolicy<br/>TokenReview"]
        RateLimit["gateway-rate-limits<br/>RateLimitPolicy<br/>free:5/2m, premium:20/2m,<br/>enterprise:50/2m"]
        TokenRateLimit["gateway-token-rate-limits<br/>TokenRateLimitPolicy"]
        Telemetry["telemetry-policy<br/>TelemetryPolicy"]
        LimitadorMetrics["limitador-metrics<br/>ServiceMonitor"]
    end

    subgraph "Consumed CRDs"
        LLMISVC["LLMInferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1"]
        ISVC["InferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1"]
        HTTPRoute["HTTPRoute<br/>gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1"]
    end

    Client[External Client] -->|HTTPS/443| Gateway
    Gateway -->|enforces| AuthPolicy
    Gateway -->|enforces| RateLimit
    Gateway -->|enforces| TokenRateLimit
    Gateway -->|enriches| Telemetry
    AuthPolicy -->|tier lookup callback| API
    Gateway -->|routes /v1/models, /maas-api/*| API
    MaaSAuthPolicy -->|protects| API

    API -->|watches via informer| LLMISVC
    API -->|watches via informer| ISVC
    API -->|watches via informer| HTTPRoute

    Gateway -->|routes model traffic| KServeBackend["LLMInferenceService<br/>Backend (port 8000)"]

    API -->|TokenRequest,<br/>TokenReview| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP"]

    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes| LimitadorMetrics

    %% Optional storage
    API -.->|optional| PostgreSQL["PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP"]
    API -->|default| SQLite["SQLite<br/>(embedded)"]

